#: ../../userguide/viewmonitors.rst:14
msgid ""
"Name: Click on any available monitor Name such as :guilabel:`Driveway` to"
" display a live feed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../userguide/viewmonitors.rst:15
msgid ""
"Thumbnail: Click on any available monitor thumbnail image to display a "
"live feed."
